{"tid":1199690,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"可能你同我一樣好驚聽晚/朝守住立法會入有危險","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T04:21:41.000Z","uid":36671,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e75d478b9767f2bb922c18ba0e5d421274252885","tid":1199690,"uid":36671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"由雨傘開始，我都唔係最前線，守下物資站，行行企企，有事閃先，除咗一次意外上咗第四五排我先知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">越多人越唔驚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>1) 越多人越清唔到，塞鳩住係到係屈機</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想講，其實聽晚我都好撚驚，<br />\n但有一個事實就係，就算唔係前線，都可以係後面頂住，有後面，前線先唔會驚。<br />\n<br />\n如果你驚，不如 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打畀琴日同你出嚟遊行班friend</span></strong>叫佢地陪你，根本好多人想出又驚，咁不如一齊驚。到好多人個陣你就會諗: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驚閪咩？！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅一班朋友，請一齊支持前線，望住前線受傷，其實多你同你個friend 可能就冇事<br />\n<br />\n聽朝可能已經比警犬封死，所以我揀聽晚1-2點到<br />\n你地唔好唔嚟呀，我會好驚架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11aa5056d3d1081fb3cbff661adf7a1391bc72b4","tid":1199690,"uid":140999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82987581e836ee5122499193a194fef83d46e8b3","tid":1199690,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQip62x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQip62x.png&h=3b7750c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夠人就唔洗驚"},{"pid":"e83dd005d4b79455b5d2d24019c65f61e9a5cfda","tid":1199690,"uid":36671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"93812ea4fd2c510c264342595032e18e9ceb4b3d","tid":1199690,"uid":36671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6df242f80f5bfdb5cc3d3dce35c8e14dbebea66","tid":1199690,"uid":36671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e21986ed605a3b0c68ddf1f7dc82d1e307b3b53","tid":1199690,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b259c0eec0623c385020bc358c9c2d2905110e","tid":1199690,"uid":36671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f6b44d4c99f66b436a23fa8e0e27013d7c4dcc","tid":1199690,"uid":36671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6517b923f6ec29a56c7001b43bab2f9f71188757","tid":1199690,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"聽晚係無衝突發生，無權拉你的"},{"pid":"8442822fad8f171c95f3f36d0cf4254b4ce06f82","tid":1199690,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score